I"ì<p>Selected papers from the 20th annual AAPAE Conference have just been published in Volume 12 of <em>Research in Ethical Issues in Organizations</em> (REIO). Topics covered include athletes as role models, sports ethics and sports governance, the separation of powers as an integrity mechanism, and virtues in just war theory. Access to REIO is through Emerald Insight.</p>

<h2 id="volume-12-achieving-ethical-excellence">Volume 12: Achieving Ethical Excellence</h2>

<p>Editors: Michael Schwartz, Howard Harris and Alan Tapper</p>

<p>Publication date: 7 October 2014</p>

<p>ISBN: 9781784412456</p>

